  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The objective of this study is to test the efficacy of a Mindfulness Based Stress Reduction
      program in COPD on quality of life, dyspnea, daily physical activity and mindfulness during
      daily life.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
